    <item>
      <title>寒冷天气预报和供应风险导致欧洲天然气价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/european-gas-prices-fluctuate-with-more-cold-weather-on-the-way</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于预测寒冷天气将进一步加剧，且供应风险将导致全球天然气市场收紧，欧洲天然气价格上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/european-gas-prices-fluctuate-with-more-cold-weather-on-the-way</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 08:24:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Orcel 推动交易，UniCredit 提出 110 亿美元收购 BPM</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/unicredit-launches-takeover-bid-for-domestic-rival-banco-bpm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利联合信贷银行 (UniCredit SpA) 以 100 亿欧元（106 亿美元）的全股票价格收购国内竞争对手 Banco BPM，开辟了第二条重大收购战线，其首席执行官 Andrea Orcel 也在竞购德国商业银行 (Commerzbank AG)。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/unicredit-launches-takeover-bid-for-domestic-rival-banco-bpm</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 05:14:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪领导的政党赢得关键州选举，印度股市延续涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/india-stocks-extend-rally-as-modi-s-party-wins-key-state-polls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的印度人民党领导的联盟在印度最富裕的马哈拉施特拉邦取得压倒性胜利，印度股市基准指数周一飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/india-stocks-extend-rally-as-modi-s-party-wins-key-state-polls</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 04:02:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
